Package: stardogR
Type: Package
Title: R wrapper for the Stardog HTTP API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Catherine", "Dalzell", email = "catherine.dalzell@stardog.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: <catherine.dalzell@stardog.com>
Description: Supplies many of the calls from the Stardog HTTP API, especially those intended
    for use in data science. Admin functions to assign users and roles, or deal with security
    are not included.
